Shell script to create sigma file from various data sets

Main settings edit cinfigure. See the script for detailed settings.

To distinguish which script (dataset) was created from
A value is entered in usrid of the sigma file. ID is script
Is distinguished by the SCRIPT ID written on the second line (usrid in namelist).
Enter 99 if nothing is set.

We recommend that you set the ID for each script, because you will not be able to distinguish them later.

